737
00:52:34.901 --> 00:52:36.403
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL LAMANG

738
00:52:38.321 --> 00:52:39.614
Paano ako makakapasok dito?

739
00:52:44.828 --> 00:52:45.829
Hindi ka pwede dito!

740
00:52:47.664 --> 00:52:48.498
